intent.user_query: What is the number of rows inserted for the utility for a timestamp

phases.goal: Execute SQL query for  on dbc: SELECT SUM(RowsInserted),FROM_TZ(CAST(CollectTimeStamp AS TIMESTAMP), 'America/Los_Angeles')  FROM td_metric_svc.dbqlutilityV WHERE EXTRACT(month FROM TheDate) = EXTRACT(month FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY 2;

arguments.sql: SELECT SUM(RowsInserted),FROM_TZ(CAST(CollectTimeStamp AS TIMESTAMP), 'America/Los_Angeles')  FROM td_metric_svc.dbqlutilityV WHERE EXTRACT(month FROM TheDate) = EXTRACT(month FROM CURRENT_DATE) GROUP BY 2;

phases.goal: Generate the final report based on the query results.
